Use ESP32 Espressif Flash Download Tool provided or download it from official page.
  Select the .bin file, select ESP32-D2WD in Develop mode.
  Select SPI speed 80 MHz.
  Select SPI Mode DIO
  Select "DoNotChgBin".
Select the .bin file @ 0x0 address.
  Select the proper COM port.
  Baud: 921600

Start.
  Wait untill it is finished!
  If necessary, apply RESET to the ESP32
  
